<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Affiliations">Affiliations</span></h2>
<p>The Museum is affiliated with: <a href="/wiki/Canadian_Museums_Association" title="Canadian Museums Association">Canadian Museums Association</a> (CMA), <a href="/wiki/Canadian_Heritage_Information_Network" title="Canadian Heritage Information Network">Canadian Heritage Information Network</a> (CHIN), and <a href="/wiki/Virtual_Museum_of_Canada" title="Virtual Museum of Canada">Virtual Museum of Canada</a>.</p>
